  "title": "fix(infinite-hits): Remove hitsPerPage option",
  "body": "hitsPerPage is an option of the `hits` and `infiniteHits` that we decided we should move away from. The reason is that there are already many ways to define it, and it's not always clear why it should be on those widgets.\r\n\r\nThe migration guide and examples have been updated accordingly.",
